{"tid":2384430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"最美港姐，成功之路。「回顧近況」有文化有氣質！","createTime":"2021-01-28T14:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T15:39:07.000Z","uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16c155b6ac3bd3243d9c475332408b1925677a39","tid":2384430,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣有「最美港姐」封號，08年嫁給身家200億的香港船王之孫許晉亨，11年誕下豪門接班人囝囝許建彤（Jayden），婚後李嘉欣淡出娛樂圈相夫教子，享受家庭樂，得閒扮靚做運動，所以50歲仍keep得好好，今個聖誕李嘉欣更一改形象試新嘢，留了多年黑色長髮的她，染上粉紅色頭髮，更與老公許晉亨孖住坐在家中聖誕樹前合照，本來一張恩愛合照，卻惹來大量負評。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5rxfwK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5rxfwK.png&h=5e9f5c30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOdvMDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOdvMDq.jpg&h=f31d4449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年點解退出娛樂圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17b4265d633ad7cc2f54063081cf451d2339e66","tid":2384430,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人知當年衰咩？"},{"pid":"a35d2951c904b4419b397d41e027950da86b9d16","tid":2384430,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1850c3fdc6f2b2032374ad1530bcc0133cae3903","tid":2384430,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce914cfdad62d54a4ee51b3770c26527e573af95","tid":2384430,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma